Usage: trim_pg_library [-help] [-delete_cells <string>]
                       [-delete_cells_file <string>] -library_list_file <string>
                       [-output <string>] -output_library <string>

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-delete_cells <string>          # cellName (string, optional)
-delete_cells_file <string>     # cellNameFile (string, optional)
-library_list_file <string>     # <absolute library path> (string, required)
-output <string>                # <directory name> (string, optional)
-output_library <string>        # newLibraryName (string, required)